---
/**
 * Footer-area tip CTA. Links out to wtpppa.org/contribute (Squarespace
 * donation page) where Apple Pay / card / etc. work natively. Cross-origin
 * embed of Squarespace donation blocks is unreliable, so the click sends
 * users to the working flow on the party site.
 *
 * Drop above the existing <footer> on any dashboard page.
 */
---

<section class="border-t border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-wtp-navy/40 to-transparent px-6 py-10 md:py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-start gap-5 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
    <div>
      <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white sm:text-xl">Found this useful? Tip the team.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-wtp-cream/70 sm:text-base">
        These dashboards are built and maintained by volunteers. A few bucks helps keep them running and free.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a
      href="https://www.wtpppa.org/contribute"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="inline-flex flex-shrink-0 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-wtp-sky px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-wtp-navy no-underline transition hover:bg-wtp-sky/90"
    >
      Tip the team
      <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
